    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References/>
      <Content>The series of meanings in {D:28.79} differs significantly from the meaning of ἐγκρύπτω in {D:85.50}. In {D:28.79} the focus in concealment is upon preventing knowledge about something, while in {D:85.50} the concealment focuses upon something being in a place where it is no longer visible.</Content>
    </Note>
