          </LEXSubDomains>
          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-10-26 11:25:53" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to cause to be safe or protected by hiding, in some contexts with the intent of not being found</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to keep safe</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to cause to be protected</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to protect</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to hide</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>Since κρύπτω also means ‘to make invisible,’ some scholars believe that this statement in {S:05100300300014} means that ‘your life is concealed in Christ’ or ‘… hidden from view …’ (see {D:24.30}). For another interpretation of κρύπτω in {S:04001304400016}, see {D:24.29}.</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
          </LEXSenses>
